UNE SÉLECTION DE QUALITÉ

Choose accorde un soin particulier à sélectionner les plus belles pépites dans tous les univers : déco, beauté, mode, maquillage, maison.. - Déco : Maison Nomade, Kipli, Tip toe, Ripaton, Bloon..
- Mode : Wild, Surfrider, Maison Kitsune, Patagonia..
- Beauté : Oden, Nuud, Prescription Lab, My Little box, oOlution..
- Épicerie : Frichti, Kalios, La Maison du chocolat, Gallia, Quitoque..
et bien d’autres.

Notre savoir-faire : être en contact avec tous les créateurs, les marques et les maisons de la terre entière. Tout ça pour vous présenter le plus rapidement possible, les produits les plus cools, au meilleur prix.

- Decor: Maison Nomade, Kipli, Tip toe, Ripaton, Bloon...

Choose is an application dedicated to surprising you every day. This is a digital concept store where you will find new exclusives daily. EXCLUSIVE ADVANTAGES

At Choose, we always manage to find a little extra something for each sale (a discount, free delivery, a small surprise in your package...). The vision? Allow you to discover or rediscover quality brands at low prices all year round.

ACCESSIBLE EVERYWHERE

By downloading the application on your mobile phone or tablet, you can take advantage of all our exclusive offers wherever you are: quietly sat on your sofa, at work (after the lunch break), or even on vacation with your feet up on the other side of the world.

- an experience that could not be simpler (not to say basic)
- delivery faster than setting up a camping tent
- brands that will get you to say "oh, where does this wonder come from?”

creator: Choose
descriptionHtml:
Lead in:
We believe that a new kind of shopping is possible.

Where you don’t seek, you find.
Where you meet stories behind products.
Where trust is non-negotiable.
Where scrolling is finite.
Where you come as you are.
Where pleasure is the only thing that matters.
We are humans who choose.


QUALITY SELECTION
Choose is a digital concept store where inspiration is a priority. We carefully select the most inspiring, reliable, and trend worthy lifestyle brands spanning beauty, fashion, home decor, and food.

ACCESS TO EXCLUSIVE OFFERS
We drop new brands daily with exclusive offerings from discounts, gifts with purchase and more; available only on Choose. Whether you’re looking to treat yourself or a loved one, we have it all.

ONE-CLICK SHOPPING EXPERIENCE
Our obsession? To be the best mobile shopping experience in the world. We’ve built a user-friendly application with superior customer service and lightning speed delivery.

ACCESSIBLE EVERYWHERE

By downloading the application on your mobile phone or tablet, you can take advantage of all our exclusive offers anytime, anywhere: walking your dog, sitting poolside in St. Tropez, or the subway ride to work.

OUR GUARANTEES:
- an experience that could not be simpler
- delivery faster than setting up a camping tent
- brands that will get you to say "oh, where does this wonder come from?”

In short, Choose offers you the opportunity to discover new designers, new trends, and to support emerging brands... all in the palm of your hand. Our savoir-faire: to deliver the most inspiring designers, brands and companies all over the world. We curate, you choose.
